  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-platform support (Kick, Twitch, YouTube, Rumble, TikTok)",
    "No API keys required - uses public endpoints and HTML parsing",
    "Real-time alerts with 60-second polling",
    "Modern Discord UI with buttons, select menus, and rich embeds",
